###########################################################
#
# Atomic for GBA
#
###########################################################
First Release 2024/07/11

[description]
KAtomic clone for GBA(Game Boy Advance)
developed on mgba

KAtomic: https://github.com/KDE/katomic

[build]
1. install DevKitPro(DevKitARM)
2. set environment variable(DEVKITARM/DEVKITPRO)
3. download butano engine -> https://github.com/GValiente/butano
   *developed on butano-17.7.0
4. put "atomic_gba" under "butano/"
5. cd butano/atomic_gba
6. make

[execute]
# simple
mgba ./atomic_gba.gba

# double the screen size
mgba -2 ./atomic_gba.gba

# output log
mgba -l 4 ./atomic_gba.gba 

[key controls]
UP/DOWN/LEFT/RIGHT : Move
A: Select Atom
B: Deselect Atom
Select: Display the final image
Start: Return to top

[LICENSE]
Basically, Follows the KAtomic license.
